OL,3,CInflation eases and hopes rise - can
OL,4,Cthe economy turn a corner in 2026?
OL,6,FThe Bank of England has already said
OL,7,Fthat decisions Rachel Reeves took in
OL,8,Fher Budget last month - freezing rail
OL,9,Ffares, removing green levies from
OL,10,Fenergy bills and extending the fuel
OL,11,Fduty freeze - should help push
OL,12,Finflation lower in the new year, at
OL,13,Fleast temporarily.
OL,15,FBut there is a less encouraging
OL,16,Freading of today's data. Heavy
OL,17,Fdiscounting before Christmas suggests
OL,18,Fretailers are having to work hard to
OL,19,Fpersuade households to spend - a
OL,20,Freminder that confidence remains
OL,21,Ffragile and economic growth weak.
