OL,3,CInflation eases and hopes rise - can
OL,4,Cthe economy turn a corner in 2026?
OL,6,FThat broader picture was reinforced
OL,7,Fyesterday when we learned that
OL,8,Funemployment has crept up to its
OL,9,Fhighest level in a decade.
OL,11,FSo while the direction of travel on
OL,12,Finflation is clearly positive, the
OL,13,Fwider economy still lacks sparkle.
OL,15,FThe Bank of England is widely expected
OL,16,Fto cut interest rates on Thursday,
OL,17,Fwith some economists forecasting
OL,18,Ffurther cuts in the new year.
