OL,6,FAnna Leach, chief economist at the
OL,7,FInstitute of Directors, laid out her
OL,8,Fbest possible scenario for the economy
OL,9,Fin 2026
OL,11,FAnna Leach, chief economist at the
OL,12,FInstitute of Directors, argues there
OL,13,Fare reasons to be hopeful now that the
OL,14,FBudget is done and the prolonged
OL,15,Fspeculation about tax rises has
OL,16,Fsubsided.
OL,18,FShe sketches out a best-case scenario
OL,19,Ffor 2026.
