OL,3,CInflation eases and hopes rise - can
OL,4,Cthe economy turn a corner in 2026?
OL,6,F"You get faster progress on planning
OL,7,Freform, the construction sector
OL,8,Frecovering, more housing market
OL,9,Factivity - a pick-up in all the things
OL,10,Fthat reflect people feeling better,
OL,11,Fand then reinforce that confidence.
OL,12,FRetail sales rise, consumer confidence
OL,13,Frecovers, business confidence turns a
OL,14,Fcorner. No more triggers for worries
OL,15,Fabout the policy environment."
OL,17,FCan she see that happening?
OL,19,F"It could happen. I'm an optimist."
